from claudio oliveira egalon subject re vulcan no not spock or haphaestu another legend with the name vulcan wa the planet much like earth in the same orbit there wa a science fiction movie sometime ago i do not remember it name about a planet in the same orbit of earth but hide behind the sun so it could never be visible from earth turn out that that planet wa the exact mirror image of earth and all it inhabitant look like the earthing with the difference that their organ wa in the opposite side like the heart wa in the right side instead in the leave and they would shake hand with the leave hand and so on claudio oliveira egalon 